{
  "video_id": "jxKUDXrtDFI",
  "title": "Thomas Hellum: The world's most boring television ... and why it's hilariously addictive",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13167.0,
      "end_time": 14474.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14474.0,
      "end_time": 15983.0,
      "text": "I have only got 18 minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15983.0,
      "end_time": 18832.0,
      "text": "to explain something that lasts for hours and days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18832.0,
      "end_time": 21102.0,
      "text": "so I'd better get started."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21102.0,
      "end_time": 25959.0,
      "text": "Let's start with a clip from Al Jazeera's Listening Post."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26649.0,
      "end_time": 30496.0,
      "text": "Richard Gizbert: Norway is a country that gets relatively little media coverage."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30496.0,
      "end_time": 33487.0,
      "text": "Even the elections this past week passed without much drama."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33487.0,
      "end_time": 36145.0,
      "text": "And that's the Norwegian media in a nutshell:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36145.0,
      "end_time": 37622.0,
      "text": "not much drama."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37622.0,
      "end_time": 38959.0,
      "text": "A few years back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38959.0,
      "end_time": 41416.0,
      "text": "Norway's public TV channel NRK"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41416.0,
      "end_time": 45593.0,
      "text": "decided to broadcast live coverage of a seven-hour train ride --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45593.0,
      "end_time": 47894.0,
      "text": "seven hours of simple footage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47894.0,
      "end_time": 50123.0,
      "text": "a train rolling down the tracks."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50123.0,
      "end_time": 53985.0,
      "text": "Norwegians, more than a million of them according to the ratings, loved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53985.0,
      "end_time": 56900.0,
      "text": "A new kind of reality TV show was born,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56901.0,
      "end_time": 60360.0,
      "text": "and it goes against all the rules of TV engagement."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60360.0,
      "end_time": 62476.0,
      "text": "There is no story line, no script,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62476.0,
      "end_time": 64519.0,
      "text": "no drama, no climax,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64519.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66443.0,
      "text": "and it's called Slow TV."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66443.0,
      "end_time": 67914.0,
      "text": "For the past two months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67915.0,
      "end_time": 71507.0,
      "text": "Norwegians have been watching a cruise ship's journey up the coast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71507.0,
      "end_time": 73566.0,
      "text": "and there's a lot of fog on that coast."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73566.0,
      "end_time": 76639.0,
      "text": "Executives at Norway's National Broadcasting Service"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76639.0,
      "end_time": 80729.0,
      "text": "are now considering broadcasting a night of knitting nationwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80729.0,
      "end_time": 83210.0,
      "text": "On the surface, it sounds boring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83210.0,
      "end_time": 84509.0,
      "text": "because it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84510.0,
      "end_time": 86600.0,
      "text": "but something about this TV experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86600.0,
      "end_time": 88458.0,
      "text": "has gripped Norwegians."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88458.0,
      "end_time": 91615.0,
      "text": "So we sent the Listening Post's Marcela Pizarro to Oslo"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91615.0,
      "end_time": 94146.0,
      "text": "to find out what it is, but first a warning:"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94146.0,
      "end_time": 98649.0,
      "text": "Viewers may find some of the images in the following report disappointing."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98649.0,
      "end_time": 99664.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100340.0,
      "end_time": 103550.0,
      "text": "Thomas Hellum: And then follows an eight-minute story on Al Jazeera"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103550.0,
      "end_time": 106875.0,
      "text": "about some strange TV programs in little Norway."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106876.0,
      "end_time": 109934.0,
      "text": "Al Jazeera. CNN. How did we get there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109934.0,
      "end_time": 111954.0,
      "text": "We have to go back to 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111954.0,
      "end_time": 113952.0,
      "text": "when one of my colleagues got a great idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113953.0,
      "end_time": 115756.0,
      "text": "Where do you get your ideas?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115756.0,
      "end_time": 117237.0,
      "text": "In the lunchroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117737.0,
      "end_time": 120714.0,
      "text": "So he said, why don't we make a radio program"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 120714.0,
      "end_time": 124298.0,
      "text": "marking the day of the German invasion of Norway in 1940."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124299.0,
      "end_time": 128343.0,
      "text": "We tell the story at the exact time during the night."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 128342.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130506.00000000001,
      "text": "Wow. Brilliant idea, except"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 130507.0,
      "end_time": 133410.0,
      "text": "this was just a couple of weeks before the invasion day."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 133410.0,
      "end_time": 135755.0,
      "text": "So we sat in our lunchroom and discussed"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 135755.0,
      "end_time": 139963.0,
      "text": "what other stories can you tell as they evolve?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139963.0,
      "end_time": 144101.0,
      "text": "What other things take a really long time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144421.0,
      "end_time": 146737.0,
      "text": "So one of us came up with a train."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 146737.0,
      "end_time": 150728.0,
      "text": "The Bergen Railway had its 100-year anniversary that year"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150729.0,
      "end_time": 153424.0,
      "text": "It goes from western Norway to eastern Norway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153424.0,
      "end_time": 157587.0,
      "text": "and it takes exactly the same time as it did 40 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157587.0,
      "end_time": 160785.0,
      "text": "over seven hours. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160785.0,
      "end_time": 163771.0,
      "text": "So we caught our commissioning editors in Oslo, and we said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 163771.0,
      "end_time": 166757.0,
      "text": "we want to make a documentary about the Bergen Railway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166758.0,
      "end_time": 168710.0,
      "text": "and we want to make it in full length,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168710.0,
      "end_time": 170640.0,
      "text": "and the answer was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170640.0,
      "end_time": 171999.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, but how long will the program be?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 171999.0,
      "end_time": 173857.0,
      "text": "\"Oh,\" we said, \"full length.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173857.0,
      "end_time": 175349.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, but we mean the program.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 175349.0,
      "end_time": 177456.0,
      "text": "And back and forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 177456.0,
      "end_time": 182942.0,
      "text": "Luckily for us, they met us with laughter, very, very good laughter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 182943.0,
      "end_time": 185629.0,
      "text": "so one bright day in September,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 185629.0,
      "end_time": 189614.0,
      "text": "we started a program that we thought should be seven hours and four minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189615.0,
      "end_time": 192479.0,
      "text": "Actually, it turned out to be seven hours and 14 minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 192479.0,
      "end_time": 196983.0,
      "text": "due to a signal failure at the last station."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196983.0,
      "end_time": 198957.0,
      "text": "We had four cameras,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198957.0,
      "end_time": 202263.0,
      "text": "three of them pointing out to the beautiful nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 202263.0,
      "end_time": 206233.0,
      "text": "Some talking to the guests, some information."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 206233.0,
      "end_time": 210283.0,
      "text": "(Video) Train announcement: We will arrive at Haugastøl Station."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210283.0,
      "end_time": 211650.0,
      "text": "TH: And that's about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 211651.0,
      "end_time": 213446.0,
      "text": "but of course, also"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 213446.0,
      "end_time": 217287.0,
      "text": "the 160 tunnels gave us the opportunity to do some archives."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217287.0,
      "end_time": 221183.0,
      "text": "Narrator [in Norwegian]: Then a bit of flirting while the food is digested."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 222483.0,
      "end_time": 226831.0,
      "text": "The last downhill stretch before we reach our destination."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 227901.0,
      "end_time": 231257.0,
      "text": "We pass Mjølfjell Station."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 232207.0,
      "end_time": 234614.0,
      "text": "Then a new tunnel."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 234615.0,
      "end_time": 235765.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 235765.0,
      "end_time": 239220.0,
      "text": "TH: And now we thought, yes, we have a brilliant program."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 239220.0,
      "end_time": 243619.0,
      "text": "It will fit for the 2,000 train spotters in Norway."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 243619.0,
      "end_time": 246220.0,
      "text": "We brought it on air in November 2009."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 246220.0,
      "end_time": 248667.0,
      "text": "But no, this was far more attractive."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 248667.0,
      "end_time": 252489.0,
      "text": "This is the five biggest TV channels in Norway on a normal Friday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 252489.0,
      "end_time": 254788.0,
      "text": "and if you look at NRK2 over here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 254788.0,
      "end_time": 258184.0,
      "text": "look what happened when they put on the Bergen Railway show:"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 258983.0,
      "end_time": 262709.0,
      "text": "1.2 million Norwegians watched part of this program."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 262709.0,
      "end_time": 265340.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 266624.0,
      "end_time": 268810.0,
      "text": "And another funny thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 268810.0,
      "end_time": 270757.0,
      "text": "When the host on our main channel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 270757.0,
      "end_time": 273224.0,
      "text": "after they have got news for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 273224.0,
      "end_time": 275662.0,
      "text": "she said, \"And on our second channel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 275662.0,
      "end_time": 278657.0,
      "text": "the train has now nearly reached Myrdal station.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 278657.0,
      "end_time": 281349.0,
      "text": "Thousands of people just jumped on the train"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 281350.0,
      "end_time": 285366.0,
      "text": "on our second channel like this. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 285366.0,
      "end_time": 289120.0,
      "text": "This was also a huge success in terms of social media."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 289120.0,
      "end_time": 293116.0,
      "text": "It was so nice to see all the thousands of Facebook and Twitter users"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 293116.0,
      "end_time": 295977.0,
      "text": "discussing the same view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 295977.0,
      "end_time": 300462.0,
      "text": "talking to each other as if they were on the same train together."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 300463.0,
      "end_time": 303748.0,
      "text": "And especially, I like this one. It's a 76-year-old man."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 303748.0,
      "end_time": 305428.0,
      "text": "He's watched all the program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 305428.0,
      "end_time": 309445.0,
      "text": "and at the end station, he rises up to pick up what he thinks is his luggage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 309445.0,
      "end_time": 313300.0,
      "text": "and his head hit the curtain rod,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 313300.0,
      "end_time": 315691.0,
      "text": "and he realized he is in his own living room."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 315691.0,
      "end_time": 320219.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 321426.0,
      "end_time": 326700.0,
      "text": "So that's strong and living TV."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 326700.0,
      "end_time": 329414.0,
      "text": "Four hundred and thirty-six minute by minute on a Friday night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 329414.0,
      "end_time": 331275.0,
      "text": "and during that first night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 331275.0,
      "end_time": 333828.0,
      "text": "the first Twitter message came: Why be a chicken?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 333829.0,
      "end_time": 339498.0,
      "text": "Why stop at 436 when you can expand that"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 339498.0,
      "end_time": 343159.0,
      "text": "to 8,040, minute by minute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 343159.0,
      "end_time": 345365.0,
      "text": "and do the iconic journey in Norway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 345365.0,
      "end_time": 348807.0,
      "text": "the coastal ship journey Hurtigruten from Bergen to Kirkenes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 348807.0,
      "end_time": 352361.0,
      "text": "almost 3,000 kilometers, covering most of our coast."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 352361.0,
      "end_time": 356938.0,
      "text": "It has 120-year-old, very interesting history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 356939.0,
      "end_time": 361755.0,
      "text": "and literally takes part in life and death along the coast."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 361755.0,
      "end_time": 364126.0,
      "text": "So just a week after the Bergen Railway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 364126.0,
      "end_time": 368871.0,
      "text": "we called the Hurtigruten company and we started planning for our next show."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 370820.0,
      "end_time": 372245.0,
      "text": "We wanted to do something different."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 372245.0,
      "end_time": 375526.0,
      "text": "The Bergen Railway was a recorded program."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 375526.0,
      "end_time": 377616.0,
      "text": "So when we sat in our editing room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 377616.0,
      "end_time": 380219.0,
      "text": "we watched this picture -- it's all Ål Station --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 380220.0,
      "end_time": 381728.0,
      "text": "we saw this journalist."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 381728.0,
      "end_time": 383681.0,
      "text": "We had called him, we had spoken to him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 383681.0,
      "end_time": 385537.0,
      "text": "and when we left the station,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 385537.0,
      "end_time": 388727.0,
      "text": "he took this picture of us and he waved to the camera,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 388728.0,
      "end_time": 390188.0,
      "text": "and we thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 390188.0,
      "end_time": 393440.0,
      "text": "what if more people knew that we were on board that train?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 393440.0,
      "end_time": 395286.0,
      "text": "Would more people show up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 395286.0,
      "end_time": 397259.0,
      "text": "What would it look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 397259.0,
      "end_time": 400789.0,
      "text": "So we decided our next project, it should be live."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 400789.0,
      "end_time": 405693.0,
      "text": "We wanted this picture of us on the fjord and on the screen at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 407340.0,
      "end_time": 410355.0,
      "text": "So this is not the first time NRK had been on board a ship."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 410355.0,
      "end_time": 412730.0,
      "text": "This is back in 1964,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 412730.0,
      "end_time": 414929.0,
      "text": "when the technical managers have suits and ties"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 414929.0,
      "end_time": 418969.0,
      "text": "and NRK rolled all its equipment on board a ship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 418969.0,
      "end_time": 423900.0,
      "text": "and 200 meters out of the shore, transmitting the signal back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 423900.0,
      "end_time": 426957.0,
      "text": "and in the machine room, they talked to the machine guy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 426957.0,
      "end_time": 431110.0,
      "text": "and on the deck, they have splendid entertainment."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 431110.0,
      "end_time": 436289.0,
      "text": "So being on a ship, it's not the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 437309.0,
      "end_time": 442335.0,
      "text": "But five and a half days in a row, and live, we wanted some help."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 442335.0,
      "end_time": 446498.0,
      "text": "And we asked our viewers out there, what do you want to see?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 446498.0,
      "end_time": 450610.0,
      "text": "What do you want us to film? How do you want this to look?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 450610.0,
      "end_time": 453318.0,
      "text": "Do you want us to make a website? What do you want on it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 453318.0,
      "end_time": 455556.0,
      "text": "And we got some answers from you out there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 455556.0,
      "end_time": 459806.0,
      "text": "and it helped us a very lot to build the program."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 459807.0,
      "end_time": 462662.0,
      "text": "So in June 2011,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 462662.0,
      "end_time": 466445.0,
      "text": "23 of us went on board the Hurtigruten coastal ship"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 466446.0,
      "end_time": 468164.0,
      "text": "and we set off."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 468164.0,
      "end_time": 471996.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 527373.0,
      "end_time": 531920.0,
      "text": "I have some really strong memories from that week, and it's all about people."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 531920.0,
      "end_time": 532732.0,
      "text": "This guy, for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 532732.0,
      "end_time": 535425.0,
      "text": "he's head of research at the University in Tromsø"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 535425.0,
      "end_time": 537188.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 537188.0,
      "end_time": 542710.0,
      "text": "And I will show you a piece of cloth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 542710.0,
      "end_time": 545298.0,
      "text": "this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 546378.0,
      "end_time": 547922.0,
      "text": "It's the other strong memory."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 547922.0,
      "end_time": 551776.0,
      "text": "It belongs to a guy called Erik Hansen."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 552796.0,
      "end_time": 560818.0,
      "text": "And it's people like those two who took a firm grip of our program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 560818.0,
      "end_time": 564639.0,
      "text": "and together with thousands of others along the route,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 564639.0,
      "end_time": 567519.0,
      "text": "they made the program what it became."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 567519.0,
      "end_time": 570470.0,
      "text": "They made all the stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 570470.0,
      "end_time": 573910.0,
      "text": "This is Karl. He's in the ninth grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 573910.0,
      "end_time": 576713.0,
      "text": "It says, \"I will be a little late for school tomorrow.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 576713.0,
      "end_time": 579382.0,
      "text": "He was supposed to be in the school at 8 a.m."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 579383.0,
      "end_time": 582484.0,
      "text": "He came at 9 a.m., and he didn't get a note from his teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 582484.0,
      "end_time": 584585.0,
      "text": "because the teacher had watched the program."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 584585.0,
      "end_time": 586460.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 586460.0,
      "end_time": 587719.0,
      "text": "How did we do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 587719.0,
      "end_time": 590935.0,
      "text": "Yes, we took a conference room on board the Hurtigruten."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 590935.0,
      "end_time": 594460.0,
      "text": "We turned it into a complete TV control room."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 594470.0,
      "end_time": 597100.0,
      "text": "We made it all work, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 597100.0,
      "end_time": 599259.0,
      "text": "and then we took along 11 cameras."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 599259.0,
      "end_time": 600374.0,
      "text": "This is one of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 600374.0,
      "end_time": 602347.0,
      "text": "This is my sketch from February,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 602347.0,
      "end_time": 604855.0,
      "text": "and when you give this sketch to professional people"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 604855.0,
      "end_time": 607840.0,
      "text": "in the Norwegian broadcasting company NRK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 607840.0,
      "end_time": 610240.0,
      "text": "you get some cool stuff back."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 610240.0,
      "end_time": 613631.0,
      "text": "And with some very creative solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 614201.0,
      "end_time": 616719.0,
      "text": "(Video) Narrator [in Norwegian]: Run it up and down."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 616719.0,
      "end_time": 620141.0,
      "text": "This is Norway's most important drill right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 620141.0,
      "end_time": 626540.0,
      "text": "It regulates the height of a bow camera in NRK's live production,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 626540.0,
      "end_time": 630790.0,
      "text": "one of 11 that capture great shots from the MS Nord-Norge."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 630790.0,
      "end_time": 633461.0,
      "text": "Eight wires keep the camera stable."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 633461.0,
      "end_time": 637106.0,
      "text": "Cameraman: I work on different camera solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 637106.0,
      "end_time": 640960.0,
      "text": "They're just tools used in a different context."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 640960.0,
      "end_time": 644304.0,
      "text": "TH: Another camera is this one. It's normally used for sports."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 644304.0,
      "end_time": 647903.0,
      "text": "It made it possible for us to take close-up pictures of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 647903.0,
      "end_time": 649923.0,
      "text": "100 kilomteres away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 649923.0,
      "end_time": 654358.0,
      "text": "like this one. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 654358.0,
      "end_time": 657189.0,
      "text": "People called us and asked, how is this man doing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 657190.0,
      "end_time": 660139.0,
      "text": "He's doing fine. Everything went well."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 660139.0,
      "end_time": 663372.0,
      "text": "We also could take pictures of people waving at us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 663372.0,
      "end_time": 665689.0,
      "text": "people along the route, thousands of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 665689.0,
      "end_time": 668113.0,
      "text": "and they all had a phone in their hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 668114.0,
      "end_time": 671990.0,
      "text": "And when you take a picture of them, and they get the message,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 671990.0,
      "end_time": 673954.0,
      "text": "\"Now we are on TV, dad,\" they start waving back."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 673954.0,
      "end_time": 676113.0,
      "text": "This was waving TV for five and a half days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 676114.0,
      "end_time": 678273.0,
      "text": "and people get so extremely happy"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 678273.0,
      "end_time": 683900.0,
      "text": "when they can send a warm message to their loved ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 683900.0,
      "end_time": 686609.0,
      "text": "It was also a great success on social media."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 686609.0,
      "end_time": 689418.0,
      "text": "On the last day, we met Her Majesty the Queen of Norway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 689418.0,
      "end_time": 693170.0,
      "text": "and Twitter couldn't quite handle it."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 693170.0,
      "end_time": 695386.0,
      "text": "And we also, on the web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 695386.0,
      "end_time": 700260.0,
      "text": "during this week we streamed more than 100 years of video"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 700260.0,
      "end_time": 703628.0,
      "text": "to 148 nations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 703628.0,
      "end_time": 707829.0,
      "text": "and the websites are still there and they will be forever, actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 707829.0,
      "end_time": 709734.0,
      "text": "because Hurtigruten was selected"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 709735.0,
      "end_time": 714267.0,
      "text": "to be part of the Norwegian UNESCO list of documents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 714267.0,
      "end_time": 717258.0,
      "text": "and it's also in the Guinness Book of Records"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 717258.0,
      "end_time": 720764.0,
      "text": "as the longest documentary ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 720764.0,
      "end_time": 724247.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 724247.0,
      "end_time": 727985.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 727985.0,
      "end_time": 731375.0,
      "text": "But it's a long program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 731375.0,
      "end_time": 734463.0,
      "text": "so some watched part of it, like the Prime Minister."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 734463.0,
      "end_time": 736204.0,
      "text": "Some watched a little bit more."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 736205.0,
      "end_time": 740614.0,
      "text": "It says, \"I haven't used my bed for five days.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 740614.0,
      "end_time": 745850.0,
      "text": "And he's 82 years old, and he hardly slept."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 745850.0,
      "end_time": 748441.0,
      "text": "He kept watching because something might happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 748441.0,
      "end_time": 750854.0,
      "text": "though it probably won't. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 750854.0,
      "end_time": 753503.0,
      "text": "This is the number of viewers along the route."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 753503.0,
      "end_time": 755105.0,
      "text": "You can see the famous Trollfjord"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 755105.0,
      "end_time": 759849.0,
      "text": "and a day after, all-time high for NRK2."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 759849.0,
      "end_time": 765671.0,
      "text": "If you see the four biggest channels in Norway during June 2011,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 765671.0,
      "end_time": 767968.0,
      "text": "they will look like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 767968.0,
      "end_time": 771818.0,
      "text": "and as a TV producer, it's a pleasure to put Hurtigruten on top of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 771818.0,
      "end_time": 773540.0,
      "text": "It looks like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 773541.0,
      "end_time": 776908.0,
      "text": "3.2 million Norwegians watched part of this program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 776908.0,
      "end_time": 778788.0,
      "text": "and we are only five million here."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 778788.0,
      "end_time": 781822.0,
      "text": "Even the passengers on board the Hurtigruten coastal ship --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 781822.0,
      "end_time": 783436.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) --"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 783436.0,
      "end_time": 787561.0,
      "text": "they chose to watched the telly instead of turning 90 degrees"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 787561.0,
      "end_time": 789675.0,
      "text": "and watching out the window."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 790435.0,
      "end_time": 793415.0,
      "text": "So we were allowed to be part of people's living room"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 793416.0,
      "end_time": 796173.0,
      "text": "with this strange TV program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 796173.0,
      "end_time": 799546.0,
      "text": "with music, nature, people."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 799546.0,
      "end_time": 802239.0,
      "text": "And Slow TV was now a buzzword,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 802239.0,
      "end_time": 806730.0,
      "text": "and we started looking for other things we could make Slow TV about."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 806730.0,
      "end_time": 809515.0,
      "text": "So we could either take something long and make it a topic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 809515.0,
      "end_time": 811736.0,
      "text": "like with the railway and the Hurtigruten,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 811736.0,
      "end_time": 814266.0,
      "text": "or we could take a topic and make it long."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 814267.0,
      "end_time": 816775.0,
      "text": "This is the last project. It's the peep show."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 816775.0,
      "end_time": 819560.0,
      "text": "It's 14 hours of birdwatching on a TV screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 819561.0,
      "end_time": 822742.0,
      "text": "actually 87 days on the web."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 822742.0,
      "end_time": 826363.0,
      "text": "We have made 18 hours of live salmon fishing."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 826364.0,
      "end_time": 829429.0,
      "text": "It actually took three hours before we got the first fish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 829429.0,
      "end_time": 831240.0,
      "text": "and that's quite slow."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 831240.0,
      "end_time": 836276.0,
      "text": "We have made 12 hours of boat ride into the beautiful Telemark Canal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 836276.0,
      "end_time": 839820.0,
      "text": "and we have made another train ride with the northern railway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 839821.0,
      "end_time": 843823.0,
      "text": "and because this we couldn't do live, we did it in four seasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 843823.0,
      "end_time": 847898.0,
      "text": "just to give the viewer another experience on the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 849580.0,
      "end_time": 853598.0,
      "text": "So our next project got us some attention outside Norway."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 853598.0,
      "end_time": 856483.0,
      "text": "This is from the Colbert Report on Comedy Central."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 856484.0,
      "end_time": 860280.0,
      "text": "(Video) Stephen Colbert: I've got my eye on a wildly popular program from Norway"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 860280.0,
      "end_time": 863213.0,
      "text": "called \"National Firewood Night,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 863213.0,
      "end_time": 867485.0,
      "text": "which consisted of mostly people in parkas chatting and chopping in the woods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 867485.0,
      "end_time": 871130.0,
      "text": "and then eight hours of a fire burning in a fireplace. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 871130.0,
      "end_time": 873731.0,
      "text": "It destroyed the other top Norwegian shows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 873731.0,
      "end_time": 876146.0,
      "text": "like \"So You Think You Can Watch Paint Dry\""
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 876146.0,
      "end_time": 879977.0,
      "text": "and \"The Amazing Glacier Race.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 879977.0,
      "end_time": 885182.0,
      "text": "And get this, almost 20 percent of the Norwegian population tuned in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 885182.0,
      "end_time": 886850.0,
      "text": "20 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 886850.0,
      "end_time": 890727.0,
      "text": "TH: So, when wood fire and wood chopping can be that interesting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 890727.0,
      "end_time": 892260.0,
      "text": "why not knitting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 892260.0,
      "end_time": 893978.0,
      "text": "So on our next project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 893978.0,
      "end_time": 898995.0,
      "text": "we used more than eight hours to go live from a sheep to a sweater,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 898995.0,
      "end_time": 901302.0,
      "text": "and Jimmy Kimmel in the ABC show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 901302.0,
      "end_time": 903451.0,
      "text": "he liked that."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 903451.0,
      "end_time": 910324.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 910324.0,
      "end_time": 914440.0,
      "text": "(Video) Jimmy Kimmel: Even the people on the show are falling asleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 914440.0,
      "end_time": 916319.0,
      "text": "and after all that, the knitters actually failed"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 916320.0,
      "end_time": 917996.0,
      "text": "to break the world record."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 917996.0,
      "end_time": 919342.0,
      "text": "They did not succeed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 919342.0,
      "end_time": 921585.0,
      "text": "but remember the old Norwegian saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 921585.0,
      "end_time": 923763.0,
      "text": "it's not whether you win or lose that counts."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 923763.0,
      "end_time": 926487.0,
      "text": "In fact, nothing counts, and death is coming for us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 926487.0,
      "end_time": 927930.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 927931.0,
      "end_time": 930825.0,
      "text": "TH: Exactly. So why does this stand out?"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 930825.0,
      "end_time": 934105.0,
      "text": "This is so completely different to other TV programming."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 934105.0,
      "end_time": 938847.0,
      "text": "We take the viewer on a journey that happens right now in real time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 938847.0,
      "end_time": 942424.0,
      "text": "and the viewer gets the feeling of actually being there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 942424.0,
      "end_time": 944588.0,
      "text": "actually being on the train, on the boat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 944588.0,
      "end_time": 946415.0,
      "text": "and knitting together with others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 946415.0,
      "end_time": 948872.0,
      "text": "and the reason I think why they're doing that"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 948872.0,
      "end_time": 951352.0,
      "text": "is because we don't edit the timeline."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 951352.0,
      "end_time": 953720.0,
      "text": "It's important that we don't edit the timeline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 953720.0,
      "end_time": 956919.0,
      "text": "and it's also important that what we make Slow TV about"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 956919.0,
      "end_time": 961648.0,
      "text": "is something that we all can relate to, that the viewer can relate to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 961648.0,
      "end_time": 964765.0,
      "text": "and that somehow has a root in our culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 964765.0,
      "end_time": 966491.0,
      "text": "This is a picture from last summer"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 966491.0,
      "end_time": 969680.0,
      "text": "when we traveled the coast again for seven weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 969680.0,
      "end_time": 973431.0,
      "text": "And of course this is a lot of planning, this is a lot of logistics."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 973431.0,
      "end_time": 977543.0,
      "text": "So this is the working plan for 150 people last summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 977543.0,
      "end_time": 980388.0,
      "text": "but more important is what you don't plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 980388.0,
      "end_time": 982905.0,
      "text": "You don't plan what's going to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 982905.0,
      "end_time": 985891.0,
      "text": "You have to just take your cameras with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 985891.0,
      "end_time": 987411.0,
      "text": "It's like a sports event."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 987411.0,
      "end_time": 989569.0,
      "text": "You rig them and you see what's happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 989570.0,
      "end_time": 992540.0,
      "text": "So this is actually the whole running order"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 992540.0,
      "end_time": 996501.0,
      "text": "for Hurtigruten, 134 hours, just written on one page."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 996501.0,
      "end_time": 1000553.0,
      "text": "We didn't know anything more when we left Bergen."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1000550.0,
      "end_time": 1003894.0,
      "text": "So you have to let the viewers make the stories themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1003900.0,
      "end_time": 1006129.0,
      "text": "and I'll give you an example of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1006130.0,
      "end_time": 1007894.0,
      "text": "This is from last summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1007890.0,
      "end_time": 1009747.0,
      "text": "and as a TV producer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1009750.0,
      "end_time": 1013397.0,
      "text": "it's a nice picture, but now you can cut to the next one."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1013400.0,
      "end_time": 1015140.0,
      "text": "But this is Slow TV,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1015140.0,
      "end_time": 1018814.0,
      "text": "so you have to keep this picture until it really starts hurting your stomach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1018810.0,
      "end_time": 1021170.0,
      "text": "and then you keep it a little bit longer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1021170.0,
      "end_time": 1022690.0,
      "text": "and when you keep it that long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1022690.0,
      "end_time": 1025454.0,
      "text": "I'm sure some of you now have noticed the cow."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1025450.0,
      "end_time": 1027484.0,
      "text": "Some of you have seen the flag."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1027490.0,
      "end_time": 1029896.0,
      "text": "Some of you start wondering, is the farmer at home?"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1029890.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1032336.0000000001,
      "text": "Has he left? Is he watching the cow?"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1032339.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1035567.9999999999,
      "text": "And where is that cow going?"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1035569.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1038802.9999999999,
      "text": "So my point is, the longer you keep a picture like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1038800.0,
      "end_time": 1041920.0,
      "text": "and we kept it for 10 minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 1041930.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1045640.0000000001,
      "text": "you start making the stories in your own head."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 1045640.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1049267.0,
      "text": "That's Slow TV."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 1049270.0,
      "end_time": 1054680.0,
      "text": "So we think that Slow TV is one nice way of telling a TV story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 1054680.0,
      "end_time": 1057163.0,
      "text": "and we think that we can continue doing it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 1057160.0,
      "end_time": 1061664.0,
      "text": "not too often, once or twice a year, so we keep the feeling of an event,"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 1061670.0,
      "end_time": 1064573.0,
      "text": "and we also think that the good Slow TV idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 1064570.0,
      "end_time": 1066242.0,
      "text": "that's the idea when people say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 1066240.0,
      "end_time": 1069676.0,
      "text": "\"Oh no, you can't put that on TV.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 1069680.0,
      "end_time": 1072721.0,
      "text": "When people smile, it might be a very good slow idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 1072720.0,
      "end_time": 1076972.0,
      "text": "so after all, life is best when it's a bit strange."
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 1076970.0,
      "end_time": 1078463.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 1078460.0,
      "end_time": 1085467.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}